        "body": "## 📝 Description\r\n\r\nRedesigned the navbar into a unified full-width responsive layout for improved visual hierarchy and usability.\r\n\r\n### Changes Made\r\n\r\n* Added GitGenie branding section with logo on the left\r\n* Centered navigation links for cleaner structure\r\n* Grouped CTA buttons:\r\n\r\n  * ⭐ Star on GitHub\r\n  * 📦 Install via npm\r\n  * 📖 View Docs\r\n* Improved spacing and alignment between navbar sections\r\n* Enhanced responsiveness across desktop and smaller screen sizes\r\n* Maintained consistency with the existing UI theme\r\n\r\nFixes #127\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## 🚀 Type of Change\r\n\r\n* [ ] 🐛 Bug fix\r\n* [x] ✨ New feature\r\n* [ ] 💥 Breaking change\r\n* [ ] 📖 Documentation update\r\n* [x] 🎨 Style/Refactor\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## 🧪 How Has This Been Tested?\r\n\r\n* **Node Version:** v20.x\r\n* **OS:** macOS\r\n* **Shell:** zsh\r\n\r\n### Tested On\r\n\r\n* Desktop view\r\n* Mobile responsive view\r\n\r\n### Expected Result\r\n\r\nNavbar remains visually balanced, responsive, and properly aligned across different screen sizes.\r\n\r\n### Actual Result\r\n\r\nNavbar successfully displays:\r\n\r\n* branding on the left\r\n* navigation links in the center\r\n* grouped CTA buttons on the right\r\n\r\nwith responsive behavior and improved spacing.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## ⚠️ Breaking Changes\r\n\r\n- [x] No\r\n- [ ] Yes\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## 📸 Screenshots / Logs\r\n\r\n* Desktop view\r\n<img width=\"1512\" height=\"862\" alt=\"Screenshot 2026-05-19 at 11 11 13 PM\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/1ae421cc-7298-4d3a-b841-5c12ad02ef56\" />\r\n\r\n* Mobile responsive view\r\n<img width=\"512\" height=\"786\" alt=\"Screenshot 2026-05-19 at 11 11 58 PM\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/22e0931b-eacb-4308-b539-e3a1238fbd27\" />\r\n<img width=\"514\" height=\"781\" alt=\"Screenshot 2026-05-19 at 11 12 08 PM\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/a0bbf88e-b6b4-44bd-88e8-467f94f77537\" />\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## ✅ Checklist\r\n\r\n* [x] My code follows the style guidelines of this project.\r\n* [x] I have performed a self-review of my own code.\r\n* [ ] I have commented my code, particularly in hard-to-understand areas.\r\n* [ ] I have made corresponding changes to the documentation (README.md).\r\n* [x] My changes generate no new warnings.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### ***Generated by GitGenie Contributor Suite***\r\n\n\n<!-- This is an auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->\n## Summary by CodeRabbit\n\n* **New Features**\n  * Added a mobile menu toggle with a collapsible navigation panel; selecting an item closes the menu.\n\n* **Style**\n  * Navigation repositioned to a full-width fixed top bar with blurred/translucent background.\n  * Desktop layout split into left logo, centered links, and right CTAs; hero header navigation elements streamlined.\n\n<!-- review_stack_entry_start -->\n\n[![Review Change Stack](https://storage.googleapis.com/coderabbit_public_assets/review-stack-in-coderabbit-ui.svg)](https://app.coderabbit.ai/change-stack/gunjanghate/GitGenie/pull/131?utm_source=github_walkthrough&utm_medium=github&utm_campaign=change_stack)\n\n<!-- review_stack_entry_end -->\n<!-- end of auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->",
